- To avoid certain objects being rebased, put &quot;REBASE_IGNORE&quot; in the object's name
- To avoid certain cameras being rebased, put &quot;REBASE_IGNORE&quot; in the camera name</locale_1033>
      </help_text>
      <button_text>
        <locale_1033>RebaseFile</locale_1033>
      </button_text>
